to take care of his dad's parents.

50
00:03:01,860 --> 00:03:03,020
It's heartbreaking for the old folks,

51
00:03:03,700 --> 00:03:04,480
and just as much for Lin.

52
00:03:25,600 --> 00:03:26,579
You blew your cover

53
