227
00:13:23,820 --> 00:13:24,560
I'll have to think about it.

228
00:13:28,440 --> 00:13:28,900
Alright then.

229
00:13:31,020 --> 00:13:32,000
Well,

230
00:13:32,900 --> 00:13:33,620
