and see how it goes.

266
00:16:07,740 --> 00:16:08,800
That's exactly right.

267
00:16:09,560 --> 00:16:10,480
When I was young,

268
00:16:10,780 --> 00:16:11,680
I learned that lesson the hard way.

269
00:16:13,100 --> 00:16:13,960
